> Using Exclusion_chain

# Tests: Edge case expanded tests — generated 2026-03-27

## Test: edg_001 — Extreme gross income ($54,705) — 10× highest eligibility standard; no optional exclusions. Result: (54705 - 65) × 0.5 = $27,320.00

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestEdg001:
  result scope Exclusion_chain.ExclusionChainDecision

scope TestEdg001:
  definition result.gross_earned_income equals $54,705
  definition result.federal_exclusions equals $0
  definition result.eitc_exclusion equals $0
  definition result.irregular_earned_income equals $0
  definition result.student_earned_income equals $0
  definition result.student_monthly_limit equals $0
  definition result.non_needs_based_unearned_remainder equals $0
  definition result.impairment_work_expenses equals $0
  definition result.blind_work_expenses equals $0
  definition result.self_support_exclusion equals $0
  assertion (result.adjusted_earned_income = $27,320)
```

## Test: edg_002 — All 10 exclusion steps: federal ($500), EITC ($300), irregular ($10), student ($1,000), $20 general, $65 earned, IRWE ($200), one-half, blind work ($100), self-support ($50). Result: $3,802.50

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestEdg002:
  result scope Exclusion_chain.ExclusionChainDecision

scope TestEdg002:
  definition result.gross_earned_income equals $10,000
  definition result.federal_exclusions equals $500
  definition result.eitc_exclusion equals $300
  definition result.irregular_earned_income equals $10
  definition result.student_earned_income equals $1,000
  definition result.student_monthly_limit equals $2,410
  definition result.non_needs_based_unearned_remainder equals $20
  definition result.impairment_work_expenses equals $200
  definition result.blind_work_expenses equals $100
  definition result.self_support_exclusion equals $50
  assertion (result.adjusted_earned_income = $3,802.50)
```

## Test: edg_003 — Student earned income exactly at monthly limit ($2,410 = $2,410 cap): full $2,410 excluded, cap does not reduce. Result: (5000 - 2410 - 20 - 65) × 0.5 = $1,252.50

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestEdg003:
  result scope Exclusion_chain.ExclusionChainDecision

scope TestEdg003:
  definition result.gross_earned_income equals $5,000
  definition result.federal_exclusions equals $0
  definition result.eitc_exclusion equals $0
  definition result.irregular_earned_income equals $0
  definition result.student_earned_income equals $2,410
  definition result.student_monthly_limit equals $2,410
  definition result.non_needs_based_unearned_remainder equals $20
  definition result.impairment_work_expenses equals $0
  definition result.blind_work_expenses equals $0
  definition result.self_support_exclusion equals $0
  assertion (result.adjusted_earned_income = $1,252.50)
```

